window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A new world. A magical sword. A kingdom in peril.</b></p><p> </p><p>When Yorick moves into his grandfather's house and discovers a magical sword, he opens a portal into a fantasy realm known as Exigen. </p><p> </p><p>Talk about being thrown into the deep end. If he wants to survive, he must battle monsters, level up, and learn to avoid vicious tentacle monsters. </p><p> </p><p>With the fate of the Kingdom in peril, only Yorick and his enchanted sword can save the princess and thwart the forces of evil.</p><p> </p><p><b>Join the adventure of a lifetime in this new action-packed isekai LitRPG adventure from Ryan Rimmel, bestselling author of Noobtown.</b></p>"; 
